          <h1 class="display-3 fw-semibold mb-2">Ethical. Loving. <em>Trusted.</em></h1>
          <p class="fs-5 mb-4">
            Dedicated to raising happy, healthy puppies in loving homes. We believe in responsible
            breeding, lifelong care, and building bonds that last a lifetime.
          </p>
          <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-2">
            <button class="btn btn-lg btn-light rounded-pill py-3 px-4">
              View Puppies<i class="ri-arrow-right-line ms-1"></i>
            </button>
            <button class="btn btn-lg btn-outline-light rounded-pill py-3 px-4">
              <i class="ri-information-2-line me-1"></i>Learn More
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 order-1 order-md-2 pt-4 px-4 pb-0" style="min-height: 100%;">
          <img
            src="/dist/assets/img/breederspot-images/beagle-2.png"
            style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; overflow: visible;"
            alt="A Person Holding a Beagle Puppy"
          />
